title: Global Day of Coderetreat 2016 - Winnipeg, Canada
description:
Join us in Winnipeg for the Global Day of Coderetreat on Saturday, October 22nd. 
Bold Commerce (http://boldcommerce.com/) has generously offered to host us at their new space in the south end: 
 
 50 Fultz Blvd, Winnipeg, MB R3Y 0L6 (https://www.google.ca/maps?q=50+Fultz+Blvd,+Winnipeg,+MB+R3Y+0L6&um=1&ie=UTF-8&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjJ9-mJ59rOAhVGHR4KHQXCD1sQ_AUICCgB) 
 
  
 
Planning has begun for the Global Day of Coderetreat 2016 event in Winnipeg, Manitoba. 
Stay tuned for details.
